data.description: This charming corner-lot home boasts 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a mix of brick and vinyl siding. With over 1600 square feet of heated living space, it offers ample room for your family. Additionally, there's a generous 900-square-foot unfinished basement. The 11x21 primary bedroom is spacious and is conveniently located on the main floor. The living room, sized at 13x21, features beautiful hardwood floors and a cozy gas fireplace. Enjoy leisurely moments on the welcoming covered front porch. Sold "As Is"
